---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Blog
permalink: /blog/index.html
---
<section class="section">
  <div class="page-intro">
    <h1>Articles & Campaigns</h1>
    <p>Real stories from the trenches—environment chaos, CI hard lessons, and the tiny wins that build trust in releases.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="blog-list">
    {% for post in collections.blog %}
      <article class="blog-card">
        <p class="blog-card-date">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</p>
        <h2>
          <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
        </h2>
        <p class="blog-card-summary">{{ post.data.summary }}</p>
        <a class="blog-card-link" href="{{ post.url }}">Read story →</a>
      </article>
    {% else %}
      <p>No blog posts yet. Add Markdown files under <code>src/blog/</code>.</p>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
